strings: <voice_0x010013C4><se_high>Red: Ah, it's good to be back at the old gaff.
<voice_0x01001DBA><se_high>Red: ...Hold up. That's weird. Where's 'e got to?
<voice_0x01001DBB><se_high>Red: Oh well, I'm sure 'e'll turn up in 'is own sweet bleedin' time.

<voice_0x010013C5><se_high>Red: Seein' as I ain't been back in a while,
I think I might put me feet up for a bit.
<voice_0x010013C6><se_high>Red: Why don't you lot go and 'ave some fun, eh?

<voice_0x010013C8><se_low>*: Red? ...Red! Oh, um, well I, er... I mean,
yer back sooner than wot I was expectin'...

<voice_0x010013C9><se_high>Red: You jumped-up little... Who gave you
permission to sit in my chair, eh? Eh?
COS IT WEREN'T BLEEDIN' ME!

<voice_0x010013CA><se_high>Red: It ain't meant for great big lumps like you!
Five more minutes under your lazy backside,
an' the 'ole thing woulda been matchwood!

<voice_0x010013CC><se_high>Red: Call yerself a bleedin' 'enchman!?
Get back outside right now and
start keepin' watch like I told ya!
